â€¢â€¢â€¢Goal FunnelsÂ°Â°Â°
â€¢â€¢A goal funnel ({conversion funnel} is a series of interactions that lead to a goal. Such as adding a Attribute. {conversion} Basically defining and accomplishing your Goal/sâ€¢â€¢â€¢

â€¢â€¢Example:
A user opens page C with the form.
The user fills out the <label>.
The user fills out the area code field.
The user creates the form.
The user navigates through JavaScriptâ€¢â€¢â€¢
ğŸš¨ Note: This above is the Google way. How I prefer to do this. Use a Task manager, Create one for Short Term. One for Medium and Long. Then take your Biggest Goal, and brake it down to Byte Size Pieces, and place them in your categories. Personally, I choose the hardest first, and save the easiest for last.
